Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_extract...sign_level_drv(25.10)  timing_extract...sign_level_drv(25.10)

Name
       timing_extract_model_consider_design_level_drv

Syntax
       timing_extract_model_consider_design_level_drv

       {true | false}

       Default : true

       Considers  set_max_capacitance  and set_max_transition DRV constraints,
       that have been applied on the current design during model extraction.

       When set to true, these constraints applied at the design level will be
       considered during model extraction. However,  the  maximum  capacitance
       and maximum transition from various DRV constraints applied/inferred on
       the ports is considered.

       When  set to false, the software extracts the worse-case DRV values and
       the constraints applied on the current design will be ignored.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

